        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Permitting Reform and Jobs Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises and makes permanent Title 41 of the Fixing America's Surface Transportation (FAST) Act, commonly known as FAST-41. FAST-41 revised the environmental review and permitting process to expedite certain infrastructure projects.</p>]]>
        </text>
